{% extends '_z_index.html.njk' %}

{% block description %}
The red box should be painted before the blue box.

The blue box doesn't establish a stacking context.  So, the red box is stacked onto the root layer
and it's z-index is less than the blue box's one.
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<div class="abs blue">
  <div class="abs red" style="z-index: -1"></div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
